    </para>

    <para condition="html" role="usernotes">Observaes de Usurio(a): <ulink url="&blfs-wiki;/glu"/>
    </para>

  </sect2>

  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Instalao de GLU</title>

    <para>
      Instale <application>GLU</application> executando os seguintes comandos:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>mkdir build &amp;&amp;
cd    build &amp;&amp;

meson --prefix=$XORG_PREFIX -Dgl_provider=gl --buildtype=release .. &amp;&amp;
ninja</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Esse pacote no vem com uma sute de teste.
    </para>

    <para>
      Agora, como o(a) usurio(a) <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>ninja install &amp;&amp;
rm -vf /usr/lib/libGLU.a</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

  

